{"type":"message","id":"bf5e1859","parentId":"f4b2cfab","timestamp":"2026-04-14T06:44:30.116Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-14 06:43 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/2). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are the DTLX BE API Tester. Test every endpoint and seed data via API calls (NOT mongosh).\n\n## Context\n- Backend: http://localhost:3001 (already running)\n- Login: POST /api/v1/auth/signin with {\"username\":\"admin2\",\"password\":\"Admin123!\"} → accessToken\n- JWT bug: FIXED ✅ (doc._id)\n- Use AHV-Holding-DEV model\n\n## PHASE 1: Map ALL endpoints\nRead all route files to build complete endpoint list:\n```\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/router.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/education.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/operation.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/notification.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/routes/v1/system.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/src/modules/*/*.route.ts\n```\nList every endpoint with METHOD and PATH.\n\n## PHASE 2: Seed Data via API\nUse curl or fetch to seed data through HTTP endpoints. Check each module's controller/service for the correct body format:\n\n### Step 2a: Create users (admin should already exist)\n- GET /api/v1/users (to see existing users)\n- Try POST /api/v1/users to create new users\n\n### Step 2b: Create courses\n- POST /api/v1/courses (check validation from courses.validation.ts)\n\n### Step 2c: Create payments (with received_fee field)\n- POST /api/v1/payments\n\n### Step 2d: Create vehicles\n- POST /api/v1/vehicles\n\n### Step 2e: Create stadiums  \n- POST /api/v1/stadiums\n\n### Step 2f: Create